reviewText: It should advertise largely , belt is not included
Waiting forever to get this oldie, but goodie. Leslie is my go to for exercise.
Leslie is my inspiration to walk! When I grow up, I want to be Leslie ;-D. Seriously speaking, I really am seeing results. This is a DVD which I had been searching for a long time. Works for me!
The weights adds to the exercise workout.  I love Leslie Sansone attitude and it is fun to do the workouts.

Good workout with weighted hands.  It's 4 miles and moves along at a pretty fast pace.  Any time you carry weights in a workout the resistance will burn more calories and provide more stamina.  Definitely a keeper for me.
Thank you for your prompt delivery.  Everything was as expected and more!
Great workout and very easy to follow.
